## 
##     Represents a @link NXOpen::Display::RayTracedStudioPreferencesBuilder NXOpen::Display::RayTracedStudioPreferencesBuilder@endlink .
##     Ray Traced Studio Preferences controls display and output of CPU-based real-time ray tracing.
