##     Interactive NX session.  If run from a non-interactive session it will 
##     return NULL. <br> 
##      <br> To create a new instance of this class, use @link NXOpen::ViewCollection::CreateRayTracedStudioPreferencesBuilder  NXOpen::ViewCollection::CreateRayTracedStudioPreferencesBuilder @endlink  <br> 
